---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Cattery Software" description="Cattery software for cat boarding businesses. Individual enclosures, vaccination tracking, sibling pricing, and automated billing for cat-specific care.">
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-navy to-gray-900 text-white py-16">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <span class="badge-primary mb-4">Cattery Software</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Manage & Grow Your Cat Boarding Business</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8">
          Purpose-built software for catteries. Individual enclosures, species-specific vaccination tracking, multi-cat family management, and automated owner communications.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a href="/contact/" class="btn-primary text-lg px-8 py-4">Start Free Trial</a>
          <a href="/pricing/" class="btn-secondary text-lg px-8 py-4">View Pricing</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">Why You Need Purpose-Built Cattery Software</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Unlike generic scheduling tools, cattery management software understands the unique needs of feline care: individual enclosures, feeding routines, medical tracking, and multi-cat family stays. Everything lives in one secure dashboard, accessible from any device.
        </p>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
          <div class="card">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">Smart Bookings</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Real-time availability and deposit collection prevent overbooking.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">Vaccination Tracking</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Automated alerts for FVRCP, rabies, and FeLV/FIV testing requirements.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">Digital Care Sheets</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Record feedings, litter box changes, meds, and notes per cat with timestamps.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">Owner Portal</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Pet parents upload vaccination proof, pay invoices, and view photos.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">Multi-Cat Families</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Group sibling cats with shared enclosures, coordinated schedules, and family pricing.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">Reports & Analytics</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Monitor occupancy, revenue, retention, and average length of stay.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">PetCare.Software vs. Generic Systems</h2>
        <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-8">
          <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse">
            <thead>
              <tr class="border-b-2 border-gray-200">
                <th class="py-3 px-4 text-brand-navy">Feature</th>
                <th class="py-3 px-4 text-brand-navy">Generic Tools</th>
                <th class="py-3 px-4 text-brand-navy">PetCare.Software</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-100">
                <td class="py-3 px-4">Availability</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-600">Manual tracking</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-600">Real-time with sibling cat logic</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-100">
                <td class="py-3 px-4">Vaccination Alerts</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-600">None</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-600">Automatic reminders</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-100">
                <td class="py-3 px-4">Customer Portal</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-600">Basic forms</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-600">Full booking, payments, uploads</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-100">
                <td class="py-3 px-4">Task Management</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-600">Paper checklists</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-600">Digital care logs with timestamps</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">FAQs</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6 mb-8">
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">What is cattery software?</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Cattery software is a specialized management platform designed for cat boarding facilities to handle reservations, cage assignments, feeding schedules, medication tracking, vaccination records, billing, and owner communications.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">Can it handle multi-cat families?</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Yes. Group family cats in shared enclosures or book adjoining suites with shared feeding schedules. The system supports sibling pricing and linked records.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">Is it different from dog boarding software?</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Cattery software includes cat-specific features like individual housing management, species-specific vaccination requirements (FeLV, FIV testing), and litter box monitoring. PetCare.Software handles both cats and dogs if you run a mixed facility.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-red to-brand-red-dark text-white">
    <div class="container-custom text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Ready to Upgrade Your Cattery?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-white/90 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Save hours each week and deliver smoother customer experiences with PetCare.Software.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn bg-white text-brand-red hover:bg-gray-100 text-lg px-8 py-4">
        Start Your Free Trial
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
